Class MultiMethod<ReturnType>

java.lang.Object
eu.daproject.evl.MultiMethod<ReturnType>
Type Parameters:
ReturnType - the return type
Direct Known Subclasses:
Method1, Method2, Method3, Method4, Method5, Method6, Method7
public abstract class MultiMethod<ReturnType> extends Object
Main class of the EVL library providing an abstract multimethod with a dimension which represents the number of "virtual" parameters.

      public MultiMethod<ReturnType> add(Class<?> classInstance, String methodName, Class<?>... parameterTypes)
      Adds a static method.
      Parameters:
      classInstance - the class instance
      methodName - the name of the method
      parameterTypes - the parameter types of the wanted method
      Returns:
      this instance
      Throws:
      MethodNotAddedException - if the method cannot be found
      BadNumberOfVirtualParameterTypesException - if the number of virtual parameter types is not equal to the one of the first inserted method
      BadNonVirtualParameterTypesException - if the non virtual parameter types are not the same than the ones of the first inserted method
